title: I've had a string of nightmares lately, but this is the only one that made me panic

media:group.media:title: I've had a string of nightmares lately, but this is the only one that made me panic
media:group.media:description:
the string is kind of over, two days ago there was this like, finale episode dream? and like there was a whole final battle where I teamed up with the thing that was terrorizing me, and they sacrificed themselves to to beat the bigger bad. then I blacked out and when I woke up everything was good and there was the whole other half of the dream where it was the last day of school and I hung out with random people.
